        WHEN 0 THEN '-'

        INNER JOIN tenant_product tp ON tsf.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
        AND tp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsf.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
        AND tsp.is_del = 0
        INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tsf.warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt twr ON tsf.warehouse_receipt_id = twr.warehouse_receipt_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtrtd ON outtrtw.dealer_id = outtrtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intrtd ON intrtw.dealer_id = intrtd.dealer_inner_id

        LEFT JOIN tenant_order troto ON tro.order_inner_id = troto.order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_user trotu ON troto.user_id = trotu.user_inner_id

         WHERE tsf.is_del = 0

        t1.product_inner_id DESC ) TOTAL

            ts.store_name                          AS belong_store_name,
            tuaf.flow_type                         AS flow_type,

        WHEN 8 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ), intrtw.warehouse_name )
        WHEN 9 THEN '-'
        WHEN 10 THEN '-'
        WHEN 11 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 12 THEN IFNULL( tortu.user_name, tortu.user_nickname )
        WHEN 13 THEN intdtd.dealer_name
        WHEN 14 THEN outtdtd.dealer_name

        WHEN 16 THEN IF( intrtw.warehouse_type = 0, CONCAT( intrtd.dealer_name, '-', intrtw.warehouse_name ), intrtw.warehouse_name )

        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer intdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_initiator_id = intdtd.dealer_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_dealer outtdtd ON tdtdo.distr_order_target_id = outtdtd.dealer_inner_id

SELECT
            tdpj.dealer_product_code                                    AS onlineProductCode,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id                           AS onlineProductId,
            tsp.single_product_third_code                               AS onlineSingleProductCode,
            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_outer_id                    AS onlineSingleProductId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_name                                    AS productName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_name )                      AS frontCateName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tb.brand_name )                      AS brandName,
            tosp.retail_price                                           AS retailPrice,
            tosp.min_price_range                                        AS minRetailPrice,
            tosp.max_price_range                                        AS maxRetailPrice,
            CONCAT_WS('；',
                IF ( tdpj.has_express_delivery = 1, '快递发货', NULL ),
                IF ( tdpj.has_in_city_delivery = 1, '同城配送', NULL ),
                IF ( tdpj.has_pick_up = 1, '到店自提', NULL )
            )                                                           AS deliveryMethod,

            tdpj.sale_limit_type                                        AS purchaseLimitType,
            tdpj.sale_limit                                             AS purchaseLimitNum,

            tdpj.is_user_limit                                          AS specifiedUserCondition,
            tdpj.member_limit                                           AS specifiedUserType,
            tdpj.member_limit_level                                     AS specifiedUserLevel,

            tdpj.on_discount                                            AS discountType,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tpmdj.member_level )                 AS discountLevel,

            tdpj.selling_point                                          AS salePoint,
            tosp.create_date                                            AS createDate,

            tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id                    AS onlineSingleProductInnerId,
            tosaj.onlinestore_single_attr_join_id                       AS attrJoinId,
            sbca.cate_attr_inner_id                                     AS attrId,
            sbca.attr_name                                              AS attrName,
            sav.attr_value_id                                           AS attrValueId,
            sav.attr_value                                              AS attrValue,
            sav.attr_code                                               AS attrCode
        FROM
            tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON tosp.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
                AND tosp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tsp.single_product_inner_id = tosp.single_product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tp.product_inner_id = tosp.product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_attr_join tosaj ON tosaj.onlinestore_single_product_id = tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN sys_attr_value sav ON sav.attr_value_id = tosaj.attr_value_id
            LEFT JOIN sys_backend_category_attr sbca ON sbca.cate_attr_inner_id = tosaj.attr_id
                AND sbca.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_brand tb ON tp.brand_id = tb.brand_inner_id
                AND tb.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_front_cate_join tpfcj ON tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_frontend_category tfc ON tfc.cate_inner_id = tpfcj.frond_cate_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product_member_discount_join tpmdj ON tpmdj.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
                AND tpmdj.is_del = 0
         WHERE tdpj.is_del = 0
            AND tdpj.dealer_id = 1
            
            
                AND tdpj.is_complete = '1' 
        GROUP BY
        tosp.onlinestore_single_product_inner_id,
        tosaj.onlinestore_single_attr_join_id
        ORDER BY
        tdpj.dealer_product_join_id DESC

SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ( SELECT t1.warehouse_receipt_inner_id AS warehouseReceiptInnerId, t1.warehouse_receipt_outer_id AS warehouseReceiptOuterId, t4.warehouse_name AS warehouseName, t1.warehouse_receipt_type AS warehouseReceiptType, t1.receipt_status AS receiptStatus, t5.tea_name AS teaName, t1.create_date AS createDate, t1.receipt_date AS receiptDate FROM tenant_warehouse_receipt t1 LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt_detail t2 ON t1.warehouse_receipt_inner_id = t2.warehouse_receipt_id AND t2.is_del = 0 LEFT JOIN tenant_product t3 ON t2.product_id = t3.product_inner_id INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse t4 ON t1.receive_warehouse_id = t4.warehouse_inner_id AND t4.is_del = 0 LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account t5 ON t1.create_user = t5.tea_id LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_order t6 ON t1.related_id = t6.purchase_order_inner_id LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_return_order t7 ON t1.related_id = t7.purchase_return_order_inner_id LEFT JOIN tenant_requisition t8 ON t1.related_id = t8.requisition_inner_id LEFT JOIN tenant_check_stock_order t9 ON t1.related_id = t9.check_stock_order_inner_id LEFT JOIN tenant_order t10 ON t1.related_id = t10.order_inner_id WHERE t1.is_del = 0 AND t1.send_warehouse_id = -1 GROUP BY t1.warehouse_receipt_inner_id ORDER BY t1.create_date DESC ) TOTAL

SELECT
            IFNULL( SUM( flow_amount ), 0 ) AS grantScore
        FROM
            tenant_user_account_flow tuaf
                RIGHT JOIN tenant_user tu ON tuaf.user_inner_id = tu.user_inner_id
        WHERE
            tuaf.account_type = 1
          AND tuaf.flow_type NOT IN (
                                     1,
                                     3,
                                     15,
                                     13,
                                     16
            )
          AND tuaf.is_del = 0

SELECT
            IFNULL(SUM( tus.user_score ), 0 ) AS enableScore,
            IFNULL(tus.freeze_score , 0 ) AS freezeScore
        FROM
            tenant_user tu
                LEFT JOIN tenant_user_score tus ON tu.user_inner_id = tus.user_id

SELECT
        t1.warehouse_receipt_inner_id AS warehouseReceiptInnerId,
        t1.warehouse_receipt_outer_id AS warehouseReceiptOuterId,
        t4.warehouse_name AS warehouseName,
        t1.warehouse_receipt_type AS warehouseReceiptType,
        t1.receipt_status AS receiptStatus,
        t5.tea_name AS teaName,
        t1.create_date AS createDate,
        t1.receipt_date AS receiptDate
        FROM
        tenant_warehouse_receipt t1
        LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse_receipt_detail t2 ON t1.warehouse_receipt_inner_id = t2.warehouse_receipt_id
        AND t2.is_del = 0
        LEFT JOIN tenant_product t3 ON t2.product_id = t3.product_inner_id
         
                INNER JOIN tenant_warehouse t4 ON t1.receive_warehouse_id = t4.warehouse_inner_id
                AND t4.is_del = 0
             
        LEFT JOIN tenant_employee_account t5 ON t1.create_user = t5.tea_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_order t6 ON t1.related_id = t6.purchase_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_purchase_return_order t7 ON t1.related_id = t7.purchase_return_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_requisition t8 ON t1.related_id = t8.requisition_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_check_stock_order t9 ON t1.related_id = t9.check_stock_order_inner_id
        LEFT JOIN tenant_order t10 ON t1.related_id = t10.order_inner_id
         WHERE t1.is_del = 0
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
                    AND t1.send_warehouse_id = -1 
        GROUP BY
        t1.warehouse_receipt_inner_id
        ORDER BY
        t1.create_date DESC LIMIT 0,20

                    shippertw.warehouse_is_express AS shipperwarehouse_is_express,
                    shippertw.warehouse_is_pick_up AS shipperwarehouse_is_pick_up,
                    shippertw.warehouse_is_city_delivery AS shipperwarehouse_is_city_delivery
                FROM
                    tenant_self_pick_up_site tspus
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tspus.pick_up_warehouse_id = tw.warehouse_inner_id
                    AND tw.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tw.warehouse_store_id = ts.store_inner_id
                    AND ts.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_self_pick_up_site_join tspusj ON tspus.self_pick_up_site_id = tspusj.self_pick_up_site_id
                    AND tspusj.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse shippertw ON tspusj.shipper_id = shippertw.warehouse_inner_id
                    AND shippertw.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_stock_share tss ON shippertw.warehouse_inner_id = tss.warehouse_id
                    AND tss.is_del = 0
                    LEFT JOIN tenant_store shipperts ON tss.store_id = shipperts.store_inner_id
                    AND shipperts.is_del = 0
                     
                 WHERE tspus.is_del = 0
                    AND tspus.pick_up_status = 1 
                GROUP BY
                    tspus.self_pick_up_site_id,
                    shipperts.store_inner_id
            ) t1
        WHERE
            t1.distance IS NOT NULL
            AND t1.shipperdistance IS NOT NULL
        ORDER BY
            t1.distance,
            t1.shipperdistance

SELECT
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tp.product_inner_id)                                                     AS productInnerId,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tp.product_outer_id)                                                     AS productOutId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_code                                                                        AS thirdCode,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tb.brand_name)                                                           AS brandName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT vbcp.leafname)                                                           AS leafName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT vbcp.combname)                                                           AS backCateName,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_id                                                                     AS dealerProductId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id                                                               AS dealerProductOutId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_name                                                                        AS dealerProductName,
            tdpj.main_cover                                                                                 AS mainCover,
            tdpj.selling_point                                                                              AS sellingPoint,
            MIN( tosp.retail_price )                                                                        AS minPrice,
            MAX( tosp.retail_price )                                                                        AS maxPrice,
            IFNULL( tdpj.min_price, 0 )                                                                     AS retailPrice,
            IFNULL( tdpj.min_del_price, 0 )                                                                 AS delPrice,
            IFNULL( ( CASE 0
            WHEN 0 THEN SUM(ts.physical_inventory)
            WHEN 1 THEN SUM(ts.physical_inventory)
            WHEN 2 THEN vsps2.physical_inventory
            ELSE 0
            END ), 0 ) AS stockNum,
            IFNULL( tspsv.store_product_sales_volume, 0 )                                                   AS sellCount,
            tdpj.create_date                                                                                AS createDate,
            tfc.frontCateNameList                                                                           AS frontCateNameList,
            tfc.frontCateOutIdList                                                                          AS frontCateOutIdList,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_type                                                                   AS dealerProductJoinType,
            tdpj.has_express_delivery                                                                       AS hasExpressDelivery,
            tdpj.has_in_city_delivery                                                                       AS hasInCityDelivery,
            tdpj.has_pick_up                                                                                AS hasPickUp,
            tdpj.fare_template                                                                              AS freightTemplateId,
            tdpj.sale_limit                                                                                 AS saleLimit,
            tdpj.member_limit                                                                               AS memberLimit,
            tdpj.member_limit_level                                                                         AS memberLimitLevel,
            tdpj.sale_limit_type                                                                            AS saleLimitType,
            tdpj.is_user_limit                                                                              AS isUserLimit,
            tdpj.on_discount                                                                                AS hasDiscount
        FROM
            tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = tosp.dealer_product_join_id
                AND tosp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tosp.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
                AND tsp.is_enable = 1
                AND tsp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tp.product_inner_id = tosp.product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_brand tb ON tp.brand_id = tb.brand_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN v_back_cate_path vbcp ON tp.back_cate_id = vbcp.leafcateid
        -- 商品库存
            LEFT JOIN tenant_stock ts ON ts.product_id = tosp.product_id
                AND ts.single_product_id = tosp.single_product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tw.warehouse_inner_id = ts.warehouse_id
                AND tw.dealer_id = 1
            -- 商品销量
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tspsv.store_product_id,
                    SUM( tspsv.store_product_sales_volume ) AS store_product_sales_volume
                FROM
                    tenant_store_product_sales_volume tspsv
                WHERE
                    tspsv.is_del = 0
                    AND tspsv.dealer_inner_id = 1
                GROUP BY
                    tspsv.store_product_id
            ) tspsv ON tspsv.store_product_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
            -- 商品分类
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id,
                    GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_name ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id ) AS frontCateNameList,
                    GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_outer_id ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id ) AS frontCateOutIdList
                FROM
                    tenant_product_front_cate_join tpfcj
                LEFT JOIN tenant_frontend_category tfc ON tfc.cate_inner_id = tpfcj.frond_cate_id
                    GROUP BY tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id
            ) tfc ON tfc.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
            -- 商品共享库存
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    dealer_product_join_id,
                    SUM( physical_inventory ) AS physical_inventory
                FROM
                    v_single_product_stock
                WHERE
                    store_channel_type = 0
                    AND store_inner_id = null
                    AND ( warehouse_is_express = 1 OR warehouse_is_pick_up = 1 OR warehouse_is_city_delivery = 1 )
                GROUP BY
                    dealer_product_join_id
            ) vsps2 ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = vsps2.dealer_product_join_id
         WHERE tdpj.is_del = 0
            AND tp.is_del = 0
            AND tdpj.dealer_id = 1
            AND tdpj.dealer_product_join_id <= 28281510059216
            
                AND tdpj.dealer_product_join_type = 0
            
            
                AND tdpj.is_complete = '1'
            
            
            
                AND (
                    tp.third_code IN(
                    
                        '3EA332491'
                    
                    )
                    OR
                    tdpj.dealer_product_code IN(
                    
                        '3EA332491'
                    
                    )
                ) 
        GROUP BY
        tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
             
        ORDER BY
        tdpj.dealer_product_join_id DESC
        LIMIT 20

SELECT
            tvr.verification_record_id                                              AS verification_record_id,
            ifnull(tu.user_nickname, tu.user_name)                                  AS user_nickname,
            tu.user_phone                                                           AS user_phone,
            tu.user_avatar                                                          AS user_avatar,
            tvr.business_store_type                                                 AS business_store_type,
            tvr.verification_record_business_id                                     AS verificationRecordBusinessId,
            ts.store_name                                                           AS businessStoreName,
            tvr.business_date                                                       AS business_date,
            tvr.verification_record_type                                            AS verification_record_type,
            tvr.verification_record_code                                            AS verification_record_code,
            tvr.verification_record_content                                         AS verification_record_content,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_start                                              AS marketing_coupon_start,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_end                                                AS marketing_coupon_end,
            (CASE  WHEN tuc.marketing_coupon_end < now() THEN 2 WHEN tuc.marketing_coupon_start > now() THEN 6 ELSE tuc.marketing_coupon_status END) AS marketingCouponStatus,
            tvr.verification_record_state                                           AS verification_record_state,
            tor.order_outer_id                                                      AS order_outer_id,
            tor.order_inner_id                                                      AS order_inner_id,
            tor.consignee_name                                                      AS consignee_name,
            tor.consignee_phone                                                     AS consignee_phone,
            tor.consignee_selffetching                                              AS consignee_self_fetching,
            tor.actually_paid                                                       AS actually_paid,
            tspus.pick_up_name                                                      AS pick_up_name,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_start_date ELSE topd.valid_start_time END ) AS valid_start_time,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_end_date ELSE topd.valid_end_time END ) AS valid_end_time,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr1.verification_sub_record_id ) AS cancelled,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr2.verification_sub_record_id ) AS unwritten
        FROM
            tenant_verification_record tvr
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tvr.business_store_inner_id = ts.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user tu ON tu.user_inner_id = tvr.user_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN  tenant_user_coupon tuc ON tuc.user_coupon_inner_id = tvr.verification_record_business_id
            AND tuc.marketing_coupon_status IN (0, 2)

SELECT
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tp.product_inner_id)                                                     AS productInnerId,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tp.product_outer_id)                                                     AS productOutId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_code                                                                        AS thirdCode,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tb.brand_name)                                                           AS brandName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT vbcp.leafname)                                                           AS leafName,
            GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT vbcp.combname)                                                           AS backCateName,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_id                                                                     AS dealerProductId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_outer_id                                                               AS dealerProductOutId,
            tdpj.dealer_product_name                                                                        AS dealerProductName,
            tdpj.main_cover                                                                                 AS mainCover,
            tdpj.selling_point                                                                              AS sellingPoint,
            MIN( tosp.retail_price )                                                                        AS minPrice,
            MAX( tosp.retail_price )                                                                        AS maxPrice,
            IFNULL( tdpj.min_price, 0 )                                                                     AS retailPrice,
            IFNULL( tdpj.min_del_price, 0 )                                                                 AS delPrice,
            IFNULL( ( CASE 0
            WHEN 0 THEN SUM(ts.physical_inventory)
            WHEN 1 THEN SUM(ts.physical_inventory)
            WHEN 2 THEN vsps2.physical_inventory
            ELSE 0
            END ), 0 ) AS stockNum,
            IFNULL( tspsv.store_product_sales_volume, 0 )                                                   AS sellCount,
            tdpj.create_date                                                                                AS createDate,
            tfc.frontCateNameList                                                                           AS frontCateNameList,
            tfc.frontCateOutIdList                                                                          AS frontCateOutIdList,
            tdpj.dealer_product_join_type                                                                   AS dealerProductJoinType,
            tdpj.has_express_delivery                                                                       AS hasExpressDelivery,
            tdpj.has_in_city_delivery                                                                       AS hasInCityDelivery,
            tdpj.has_pick_up                                                                                AS hasPickUp,
            tdpj.fare_template                                                                              AS freightTemplateId,
            tdpj.sale_limit                                                                                 AS saleLimit,
            tdpj.member_limit                                                                               AS memberLimit,
            tdpj.member_limit_level                                                                         AS memberLimitLevel,
            tdpj.sale_limit_type                                                                            AS saleLimitType,
            tdpj.is_user_limit                                                                              AS isUserLimit,
            tdpj.on_discount                                                                                AS hasDiscount
        FROM
            tenant_dealer_product_join tdpj
            LEFT JOIN tenant_onlinestore_single_product tosp ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = tosp.dealer_product_join_id
                AND tosp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tosp.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
                AND tsp.is_enable = 1
                AND tsp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tp.product_inner_id = tosp.product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_brand tb ON tp.brand_id = tb.brand_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN v_back_cate_path vbcp ON tp.back_cate_id = vbcp.leafcateid
        -- 商品库存
            LEFT JOIN tenant_stock ts ON ts.product_id = tosp.product_id
                AND ts.single_product_id = tosp.single_product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tw.warehouse_inner_id = ts.warehouse_id
                AND tw.dealer_id = 1
            -- 商品销量
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tspsv.store_product_id,
                    SUM( tspsv.store_product_sales_volume ) AS store_product_sales_volume
                FROM
                    tenant_store_product_sales_volume tspsv
                WHERE
                    tspsv.is_del = 0
                    AND tspsv.dealer_inner_id = 1
                GROUP BY
                    tspsv.store_product_id
            ) tspsv ON tspsv.store_product_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
            -- 商品分类
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id,
                    GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_name ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id ) AS frontCateNameList,
                    GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_outer_id ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id ) AS frontCateOutIdList
                FROM
                    tenant_product_front_cate_join tpfcj
                LEFT JOIN tenant_frontend_category tfc ON tfc.cate_inner_id = tpfcj.frond_cate_id
                    GROUP BY tpfcj.dealer_product_join_id
            ) tfc ON tfc.dealer_product_join_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
            -- 商品共享库存
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    dealer_product_join_id,
                    SUM( physical_inventory ) AS physical_inventory
                FROM
                    v_single_product_stock
                WHERE
                    store_channel_type = 0
                    AND store_inner_id = null
                    AND ( warehouse_is_express = 1 OR warehouse_is_pick_up = 1 OR warehouse_is_city_delivery = 1 )
                GROUP BY
                    dealer_product_join_id
            ) vsps2 ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = vsps2.dealer_product_join_id
         WHERE tdpj.is_del = 0
            AND tp.is_del = 0
            AND tdpj.dealer_id = 1
            AND tdpj.dealer_product_join_id <= 28281509604928
            
                AND tdpj.dealer_product_join_type = 0
            
            
                AND tdpj.is_complete = '1'
            
            
                AND (
                    tp.product_name LIKE CONCAT( '%', '3EA332471', '%' )
                    OR
                    tdpj.dealer_product_name LIKE CONCAT( '%', '3EA332471', '%' )
                ) 
        GROUP BY
        tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
             
        ORDER BY
        tdpj.dealer_product_join_id DESC
        LIMIT 20

                AND tosp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_single_product tsp ON tosp.single_product_id = tsp.single_product_inner_id
                AND tsp.is_enable = 1
                AND tsp.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON tp.product_inner_id = tosp.product_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_brand tb ON tp.brand_id = tb.brand_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN v_back_cate_path vbcp ON tp.back_cate_id = vbcp.leafcateid
        -- 商品库存
            LEFT JOIN tenant_stock ts ON ts.product_id = tosp.product_id

            LEFT JOIN tenant_warehouse tw ON tw.warehouse_inner_id = ts.warehouse_id
                AND tw.dealer_id = 1
            -- 商品销量
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tspsv.store_product_id,

                FROM
                    tenant_store_product_sales_volume tspsv
                WHERE

                    AND tspsv.dealer_inner_id = 1
                GROUP BY
                    tspsv.store_product_id
            ) tspsv ON tspsv.store_product_id = tdpj.dealer_product_join_id
            -- 商品分类
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT

                    GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT tfc.cate_name ORDER BY tfc.cate_inner_id ) AS frontCateNameList,

            -- 商品共享库存

                FROM
                    v_single_product_stock
                WHERE
                    store_channel_type = 0
                    AND store_inner_id = null

                GROUP BY
                    dealer_product_join_id
            ) vsps2 ON tdpj.dealer_product_join_id = vsps2.dealer_product_join_id
         WHERE tdpj.is_del = 0
            AND tp.is_del = 0
            AND tdpj.dealer_id = 1

SELECT

            ifnull(tu.user_nickname, tu.user_name)                                  AS user_nickname,
            tu.user_phone                                                           AS user_phone,
            tu.user_avatar                                                          AS user_avatar,
            tvr.business_store_type                                                 AS business_store_type,
            tvr.verification_record_business_id                                     AS verificationRecordBusinessId,
            ts.store_name                                                           AS businessStoreName,
            tvr.business_date                                                       AS business_date,
            tvr.verification_record_type                                            AS verification_record_type,
            tvr.verification_record_code                                            AS verification_record_code,
            tvr.verification_record_content                                         AS verification_record_content,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_start                                              AS marketing_coupon_start,
            tuc.marketing_coupon_end                                                AS marketing_coupon_end,
            (CASE  WHEN tuc.marketing_coupon_end < now() THEN 2 WHEN tuc.marketing_coupon_start > now() THEN 6 ELSE tuc.marketing_coupon_status END) AS marketingCouponStatus,
            tvr.verification_record_state                                           AS verification_record_state,
            tor.order_outer_id                                                      AS order_outer_id,
            tor.order_inner_id                                                      AS order_inner_id,
            tor.consignee_name                                                      AS consignee_name,
            tor.consignee_phone                                                     AS consignee_phone,
            tor.consignee_selffetching                                              AS consignee_self_fetching,
            tor.actually_paid                                                       AS actually_paid,
            tspus.pick_up_name                                                      AS pick_up_name,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_start_date ELSE topd.valid_start_time END ) AS valid_start_time,
            ( CASE tp.coupon_validity_type WHEN 1 THEN tp.coupon_validity_end_date ELSE topd.valid_end_time END ) AS valid_end_time,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr1.verification_sub_record_id ) AS cancelled,
            COUNT( DISTINCT tvsr2.verification_sub_record_id ) AS unwritten
        FROM
            tenant_verification_record tvr
            LEFT JOIN tenant_store ts ON tvr.business_store_inner_id = ts.store_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_user tu ON tu.user_inner_id = tvr.user_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN  tenant_user_coupon tuc ON tuc.user_coupon_inner_id = tvr.verification_record_business_id
            AND tuc.marketing_coupon_status IN (0, 2)
            LEFT JOIN tenant_order tor ON tor.order_inner_id = tvr.verification_record_business_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_self_pick_up_site tspus ON tspus.self_pick_up_site_id=tor.self_pick_up_site_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_verification_sub_record tvsr ON tvr.verification_record_id = tvsr.verification_record_id
            AND tvsr.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_order_product_detail topd ON tvsr.relation_server_id = topd.order_product_detail_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_product tp ON topd.product_id = tp.product_inner_id
            LEFT JOIN tenant_verification_sub_record tvsr1 ON tvr.verification_record_id = tvsr1.verification_record_id
            AND tvsr1.verification_record_sub_state = 1
            AND tvsr1.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN tenant_verification_sub_record tvsr2 ON tvr.verification_record_id = tvsr2.verification_record_id
            AND tvsr2.verification_record_sub_state = 0
            AND tvsr2.is_del = 0
         WHERE tvr.is_del = 0
            AND tvr.verification_record_state = 0
            
                    AND ( tvr.verification_record_code = 'GMC7360338520774144'
                    OR tvsr.verification_record_sub_code = 'GMC7360338520774144'
                    )
                
            
            
            
                AND tvr.verification_record_type = 0 
        GROUP BY
            tvr.verification_record_id
        ORDER BY
         
                CASE marketingCouponStatus
                WHEN 0 THEN 0
                WHEN 6 THEN 1
                WHEN 2 THEN 2
                END,
                CASE marketingCouponStatus
                WHEN 0 THEN tuc.marketing_coupon_end
                WHEN 2 THEN tuc.marketing_coupon_end
                WHEN 6 THEN tuc.marketing_coupon_start
                END LIMIT 0,10

SELECT
            tmc.marketing_coupon_id AS couponTempNo,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_outer_id AS marketingCouponOuterId,
            tmc.marketing_activity_id AS marketingActivityId,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_name AS marketingCouponName,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_name_remark AS marketingCouponNameRemark,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_type AS marketingCouponType,
            ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_type
                WHEN 0 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN CONCAT( '减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS CHAR ) )
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS CHAR ) )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS CHAR ) )
                    END
                )
                WHEN 1 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN CONCAT( 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_discount * 10 AS CHAR ), '折' )
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_discount * 10 AS CHAR ), '折' )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_discount * 10 AS CHAR ), '折' )
                    END
                )
                WHEN 2 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN CONCAT( '随机减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS CHAR ), '-', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS CHAR ) )
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,随机减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS CHAR ), '-', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS CHAR ) )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,随机减', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS CHAR ), '-', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS CHAR ) )
                    END
                )
                WHEN 3 THEN ( CASE tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold_type
                    WHEN 0 THEN '可兑换'
                    WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '元,可兑换' )
                    ELSE CONCAT( '满', 0 + CAST( tmc.marketing_coupon_threshold AS CHAR ), '件,可兑换' )
                    END
                )
            END
            )                           AS discountsContent,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_status AS marketingCouponStatus,
            IFNULL( ( tmc.marketing_coupon_total_amount - IFNULL( surplustuc.count, 0 ) ), 0 ) AS surplusNumber,
            IFNULL( alreadyUsetuc.count, 0 ) AS alreadyUseNumber,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_deduction_amount AS marketingCouponDeductionAmount,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_discount AS marketingCouponDiscount,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_random_start AS marketingCouponRandomStart,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_random_end AS marketingCouponRandomEnd,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_start AS marketingCouponStart,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_end AS marketingCouponEnd,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_expiry_type AS marketingCouponExpiryType,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_expiry_start_day AS marketingCouponExpiryStartDay,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_expiry_day AS marketingCouponExpiryDay,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_icon_before AS marketingCouponIconBefore,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_icon_after AS marketingCouponIconAfter,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_get_user_limit AS marketingCouponGetUserLimit,
            tmc.marketing_coupon_get_limit AS marketingCouponGetLimit,
            tma.dealer_id AS dealerId,
            tma.store_id AS storeId
        FROM
            tenant_marketing_coupon tmc
            LEFT JOIN tenant_marketing_activity tma ON tmc.marketing_activity_id = tma.marketing_activity_id
            AND tma.is_del = 0
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id,
                    COUNT( tuc.user_coupon_inner_id ) count
                FROM
                    tenant_user_coupon tuc
                WHERE
                    tuc.is_del = 0
                    AND tuc.user_inner_id IS NOT NULL
                GROUP BY
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id
            ) surplustuc ON tmc.marketing_coupon_id = surplustuc.marketing_coupon_id
            LEFT JOIN (
                SELECT
                    tuc.marketing_coupon_id,
                    COUNT( tuc.user_coupon_inner_id ) count
                FROM
                    tenant_user_coupon tuc
                WHERE
